# Model config: Qwen3-Coder-Next (UD-Q4_K_XL, single-file GGUF) -- model-intrinsic only.
#
# 80B MoE, ~3B active. UD-Q4_K_XL is Unsloth's Dynamic-2.0 imatrix 4-bit quant
# (~49.6 GB, single file at the HF repo root -- no shards). It replaces the old
# Q4_1 here: near-identical size, but the UD imatrix quants benchmark measurably
# above legacy/standard quants on this model (Aider Polyglot / LiveCodeBench
# comparisons published by Unsloth + Benjamin Marie, Feb 2026), and the imatrix
# was re-cut after the Feb 4 2026 llama.cpp key_gdiff fix.
#
# Download (the file sits at the HF repo ROOT, so point --local-dir at the
# per-quant subfolder to match the on-disk layout of the other quants):
#   hf download unsloth/Qwen3-Coder-Next-GGUF \
#     --include "Qwen3-Coder-Next-UD-Q4_K_XL.gguf" \
#     --local-dir /data/models/Qwen3-Coder-Next/UD-Q4_K_XL
#
# Sampling: see models/qwen3-coder-next.env (Qwen card + Unsloth, 2026-07-17).

: "${MODEL:=Qwen3-Coder-Next/UD-Q4_K_XL/Qwen3-Coder-Next-UD-Q4_K_XL.gguf}"

LLAMA_ARGS+=(--temp 1.0 --top-p 0.95 --top-k 40 --min-p 0.01 --repeat-penalty 1.0)
LLAMA_ARGS+=(--alias qwen3-coder-next)
